Install Following :

1 . fbconsole
fbconsole is a small facebook api client for use in python scripts.

You can install fbconsole using pip:

pip install fbconsole

2. Flask Framework

pip install Flask


Then Run demo.py file using
$ python demo.py

It will first authenticate using facebook app nitzzz created by me then you can go to URL : http://127.0.0.1:5000 i.e Localhost .
After Entering status and submitting , Status will be updated on Facebook .